    'Glazed Pearl Onions': `<h2>Glazed Pearl Onions</h2><h3>Ingredients</h3><table><colgroup><col style="width: 46%"/><col style="width: 17%"/><col style="width: 17%"/><col style="width: 18%"/></colgroup><thead><tr class="header"><th>Ingredient</th><th>25</th><th>50</th><th>70</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="odd"><td>Pearl onions, peeled</td><td>5 lb</td><td>10 lb</td><td>14 lb</td></tr><tr class="even"><td>Butter</td><td>2 lb</td><td>4 lb</td><td>5.5 lb</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td>Sugar</td><td>8 oz</td><td>16 oz</td><td>22 oz</td></tr><tr class="even"><td>Chicken stock</td><td>2 qt</td><td>4 qt</td><td>5.5 qt</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td>Kosher salt</td><td>to taste</td><td>to taste</td><td>to taste</td></tr></tbody></table><h3>Method</h3><ol type="1"><li><p>Sauté onions in butter until lightly browned.</p></li><li><p>Add sugar and stock; simmer until onions are glazed.</p></li></ol>` ,
